Package: mx.client
Type: Package
Title: Stateful Matrix Client Helpers
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Troy", "Hernandez", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "troy@cornball.ai",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-4248-604X")),
    person("cornball.ai", role = "cph"))
Description: Stateful helpers for Matrix clients in R. Builds on the
    low-level 'mx.api' Client-Server API bindings with local
    configuration persistence, room resolution, sync cursor handling,
    event extraction, invite acceptance, and other reusable client
    mechanics. End-to-end encryption orchestration is planned, but
    cryptographic primitives remain in 'mx.crypto'.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/cornball-ai/mx.client
BugReports: https://github.com/cornball-ai/mx.client/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    mx.api,
    tools,
    utils
Suggests:
    tinytest
Encoding: UTF-8
